Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}片名：宇宙威龙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格?{\r}\N\NDoug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的，你还好吧{\r}\N\NHoney, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你又作梦了{\r}\N\NYou're dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格，是否又是关于火星的梦?{\r}\N\NDoug, was it about Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好点没?{\r}\N\NIs that better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可怜的宝贝{\r}\N\NMy poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些梦都快占据你的脑袋了{\r}\N\NThis is getting to be an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她也在梦里吗？{\r}\N\NWas she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁?{\r}\N\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个你对我提过的褐发女子{\r}\N\NThe one you told me about. the brunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗莉{\r}\N\NLori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不敢相信连我作梦你也会吃醋{\r}\N\NI can't believe you're jealous of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她到底是谁? - 无足轻重的人{\r}\N\N- Who is she? - Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无足轻重的人？她叫什么名字？{\r}\N\N'Nobody'? What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道{\r}\N\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 告诉我！ - 我不知道啊！{\r}\N\N- Tell me! - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你最好是告诉我！{\r}\N\NYou better tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这可不好笑，道格 你每天晚上都梦到她啊！{\r}\N\NIt's not funny, Doug. You dream about her every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我到了早上总回到你身边{\r}\N\NAnd I'm always back in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放开我！{\r}\N\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别这样，宝贝{\r}\N\NCome on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道，你才是我梦想中的女孩{\r}\N\NYou know you're the girl of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这是真心话？{\r}\N\NYou mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你很清楚我是真心的{\r}\N\NYou know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我给你的春梦提供些题材{\r}\N\NI'll give you something to dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}主席为这次攻击辩护 宣称在太空中布署的武器{\r}\N\NThe chairman defended the attack, saying that space-based weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是唯一能对付南区新兴势力的有效防御{\r}\N\Nare our only effective defense against the southern block's numerical superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}此外，火星咋晚又发生暴乱{\r}\N\NAnd more violence last night on Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要求独立的恐怖份子{\r}\N\Nwhere terrorists demanding independence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再度迫使Ｔ矿的开采停工{\r}\N\Nonce again halted the extraction of terbinium ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头和他率领的所谓自由战土{\r}\N\NKuato and his so-called freedom brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}宣称这次爆炸事件是他们所干的{\r}\N\Nclaimed credit for this latest bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}企图重新开启 已封闭的金字塔形矿坑{\r}\N\Nwhich attempted to reopen the sealed-off Pyramid Mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}火星军事当局仅以最少的兵力，就恢复当地秩序{\r}\N\NMars military restored order with minimal use of force...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有重要的战略设施，都在一小时内修复完毕{\r}\N\Nand all damage to the strategic facility was repaired within hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不准拍摄！滚！{\r}\N\NNo cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}目前已经有一处矿坑关闭 火星行政官维罗斯?科海根{\r}\N\NWith one mine already closed, mars administrator Vilos Cohaagen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}誓言在必要时仍将动用军队{\r}\N\Nvowed that troops would be used if necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以维持足额的开采量 在今天的记者会中{\r}\N\Nto keep production at full capacity. At the press conference today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}难怪你会做恶梦 你老喜欢看新闻{\r}\N\NNo wonder you're having nightmares. you're always watching the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 罗莉 - 道格？{\r}\N\N- Lori. - Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 咱们就这么办吧！ - 做什么？{\r}\N\N- Let's do it. - Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}搬到火星去住{\r}\N\NMove to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的，你为什么一定要 破坏一个如此美好的早晨呢？{\r}\N\NHoney, why do you have to spoil a perfectly wonderful morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}考虑一下吧{\r}\N\NJust think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的，我们已经谈过无数次了 你会讨厌住在火星上的{\r}\N\NSweetheart, we've been through this a million times. You'd hate it on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那里既干燥，丑陋，又无趣{\r}\N\NIt's dry, it's ugly, it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更何况… 那里随时都可能爆发革命{\r}\N\NI mean, really, a revolution could break out there any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根说那只是一小撮偏激份子{\r}\N\NCohaagen says it's just a few extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你相信他的说法？{\r}\N\NYou believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，就当我没提过此事{\r}\N\NOkay. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绝对不行！ 火星是北区投下大量经费，才殖民成功的{\r}\N\NAbsolutely not. Mars was colonized by the northern block at enormous expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们全部的军费都得依赖此地的Ｔ矿开采{\r}\N\NOur entire war effort depends on their terbinium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将这一切放弃是荒唐的想法{\r}\N\NAnd it's ridiculous to think we're going to give it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就只因为一些懒惰的变种人…{\r}\N\Njust because a bunch of lazy mutants think they own the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格，或许咱们该去做一次旅行{\r}\N\N- Doug, Maybe we should take a trip, hum? - Any comments, sir, on the rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗莉，拜托别挡住银幕{\r}\N\N- Lori, move. - that you've blown the Pyramid Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you found alien artifacts inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有许多比火星更好的地方啊！{\r}\N\NThere's a lot better places here than Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}土星怎样？ 你不想到土星去看看吗?{\r}\N\NWhat about Saturn? don't you wanna see Saturn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could find some alien artifacts. our tourist industry could use a boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家都说那里好漂亮{\r}\N\NEverybody says that its gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实是寡头先生和他的恐怖份子 企图散布这些谣言{\r}\N\NBut the fact is, it's Mr. Kuato and his terrorists who spread these rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以损害人民对政府的信任{\r}\N\Nto undermine my trust in the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以做一次长途的太空之旅 那种无须刻意做任何事的旅行{\r}\N\NWe could take a long space cruise, the kind with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说如何？{\r}\N\N- Have you found Kuato yet? - We don't even know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说什么？{\r}\N\N- What do you say? - That's all for the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我快迟到了，罗莉{\r}\N\N- Stay tuned for Christina in the weather. - I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的…{\r}\N\N- Tonight on ESPN, the fifth game of World Series... - Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,live from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:09:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格，我知道刚搬到一个新的城市 是很难适应的，但请你试试看，好吗?{\r}\N\NDoug? I know it's hard being in a new town, but let's give it a chance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗莉，你难道不明白吗? 我觉得我这辈子不该只是如此{\r}\N\NLori, don't you understand? I feel like I was made for something more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想在我的一生中有番作为 我想成为一个有用的人{\r}\N\NI want to do something with my life, I want to be somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你已经是个了不起的人了{\r}\N\NYou are somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是我爱的男人{\r}\N\NYou're the man I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\N\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祝你有个偷快的一天{\r}\N\NHave a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你现在正进入一个安全地带{\r}\N\NYou are now entering a safety zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有经核准的武器 都不得携出这检查点{\r}\N\NNo unauthorized weapons allowed beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你现在正进入一个安全地带{\r}\N\NYou are now entering a safety zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有未经核准的武器{\r}\N\NNo unauthorized weapons allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}都不得携出这检查点{\r}\N\Nbeyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是否梦想到雪地去滑雪{\r}\N\NWould you like to ski...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但却苦无门路…{\r}\N\Nbut you're snowed under with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是否梦想到海底悠游…{\r}\N\NDo you dream of a vacation at the bottom of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}却出不起旅费？{\r}\N\Nbut you can't float the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是否渴望到火星上爬山…{\r}\N\NHave you always wanted to climb the mountains of Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你的体力却已经走下坡？{\r}\N\Nbut now you're over the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就到瑞可公司来吧！{\r}\N\NThen come to Rekall Incorporated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在此可以买到 你心目中理想的假期{\r}\N\Nwhere you can buy the memory of your ideal vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比真正的旅游经验更便宜，更安全，更好{\r}\N\Ncheaper, safer and better than the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别让美好的人生从你眼前溜过{\r}\N\NSo don't let life pass you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}立刻拨电话到瑞可来 {\r}\N\NCall Rekall for the memory of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你的生命留下美好的回忆\N\NFor the memory of a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rekall, Rekall, Rekall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈利{\r}\N\NHarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你听过瑞可这个公司吧? - 瑞可?{\r}\N\N- You ever heard of Rekall? - Rekall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是专门卖假记忆的地方{\r}\N\NWhere they sell those fake memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊，瑞可！瑞可…{\r}\N\NOh, Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你想去找他们？ - 我不知道，或许吧{\r}\N\N- You're thinking of going there? - I don't know, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别去 - 为什么？{\r}\N\N- Well, don't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有一个朋友，试了他的的特殊产品 结果差点得割掉前脑{\r}\N\NA friend of mine tried one of these in a special office, nearly got himself lobotomized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的?{\r}\N\NNo shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别拿自己脑袋开玩笑，兄弟 不值得{\r}\N\NDon't fuck with your brain, pal. It ain't worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想是吧！{\r}\N\NI guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}午安，欢迎光临瑞可公司{\r}\N\NGood afternoon. welcome to Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是道格拉斯?魁德 和医生约好了{\r}\N\NDouglas Quaid. I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 鲍伯？ - 是的{\r}\N\N- Bob? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 道格?魁德来找你了 - 我马上来 - 好{\r}\N\N- Doug Quaid is here to see you. - Yeah, I'll be right out. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请稍待一下，魁德先生{\r}\N\NThat'll be just one minute, Mr. Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你{\r}\N\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 道格，我是鲍伯?麦克连，幸会 - 幸会 {\r}\N\N- Doug! Paul McClane. It's good to see ya. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到里面谈吧！这边请{\r}\N\NCome on in, through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 坐，不必拘束 - 谢谢你{\r}\N\N- Please have a seat, make yourself comfortable. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉我，道格{\r}\N\NNow, help me out here, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你想要植入的记忆是关于… - 火星{\r}\N\N- You were interested in a memory of a-- - Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊，火星…{\r}\N\NYeah. Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有困难吗？{\r}\N\NIs that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我老实告诉你好了，道格{\r}\N\NTo be perfectly honest with you, Doug...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你对外层空间感兴趣的话{\r}\N\Nif outer spaces is your thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你会更喜欢我们的土星之旅 这是目前最流行的{\r}\N\NI think you would be much happier with one of our Saturn cruises. Everybody raves about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我对土星没兴趣 我要的是火星{\r}\N\NNo, I'm not interested in Saturn. I said Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧！花钱的人是大爷{\r}\N\NOkay. You're the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么就设定在火星{\r}\N\NMars it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看看…{\r}\N\NNow, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一次标准的火星之旅{\r}\N\NThe basic Mars package...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}收费是899个信用单位{\r}\N\Nwill run you 899 credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这包括整整两个礼拜的记忆 不但完整，而且非常详细{\r}\N\NNow, that's for two full weeks of memories, complete in every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你要更久的时间就得再加钱 因为我们得植入更深{\r}\N\NIf you want a longer trip that'll cost a little more because it's a deeper implant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个礼拜的旅程里包括什么？{\r}\N\NWhat's in the two-week package?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先，我得告诉你，道格 当你到瑞可来，所得到的绝对是第一流的记忆{\r}\N\NFirst of all, Doug. Let me tell you, when you go Rekall, you get nothing but first-class memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在航天飞机上接有私人包厢 住宿希尔顿的豪华套房，加上到所有观光点游览{\r}\N\NPrivate cabin in a shuttle, deluxe suite at the Hilton Plaza, all the major sights:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}金字塔山，大运河{\r}\N\NMount Pyramid, the Grand Canals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然，还有维纳斯城{\r}\N\Nand, of course, Venusville.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但这些记忆将有多逼真?{\r}\N\NBut how real does it seem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 和你自己的记忆一样逼真 - 少来，别盖我了{\r}\N\N- As real as any memory in your head. - Come on, don't bullshit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我是说真的，道格 你的大脑将分不出它有何差别{\r}\N\NNo, I'm telling you, Doug. Your brain will not know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}信用保证，不满意可以退钱{\r}\N\NThat's guaranteed or your money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被你们切除前脑的那家伙呢？ 你们事后有退钱给他吗?{\r}\N\NWhat about the guy you lobotomized? did he get a refund?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是好久以前的事了{\r}\N\NYou're talking ancient history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在今天，以瑞可的方式旅行 比搭火箭安全多了{\r}\N\NNowadays traveling with Rekall is safer than getting on a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看看那些统计数字{\r}\N\NCheck out those statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更何况，一次真正的旅程再麻烦不过了{\r}\N\NBesides, a real holiday is a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会遗失行李，碰上坏天气...{\r}\N\NYou got lost luggage, lousy weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还会被恶出租车司机敲竹杠{\r}\N\Ncrooked taxi drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但当你以瑞可的方式旅行时{\r}\N\NWhen you travel with Rekall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一切都是完美的{\r}\N\Neverything is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说怎样？{\r}\N\NSo, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好吧 - 聪明的决定{\r}\N\N- All right. - Smart move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，在你填这份调查表的同时{\r}\N\NAll right, while you fill out this questionnaire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我顺便向你介绍一下其他的产品{\r}\N\NI'll gonna familiarize you with some of our options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要其他的产品{\r}\N\NNo options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}随便你好了 我能问你一个问题吗？{\r}\N\NWhatever you say. Can I ask you just one question, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在你以往每次的旅行中{\r}\N\NWhat is it? Is it exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}都有哪一样共同点？{\r}\N\Nabout every single vacation you have ever taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我放弃{\r}\N\NI give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你，你就是那共同点{\r}\N\NYou. You're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不论你到哪里去，你总是同一个你{\r}\N\NNo matter where you go, There you are. It's always the same old you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我建议你这回{\r}\N\NLet me suggest that you take a vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}暂且不当你自己{\r}\N\Nfrom yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道这听来很玄{\r}\N\NI know, it sounds wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是我们最新的旅行方式 我们称它叫“自我旅行”{\r}\N\NIt is the latest thing in travel. we call it the Ego Trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我对这没有兴趣{\r}\N\NNo, I'm not interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会喜欢它的，道格{\r}\N\NYou're gonna love this, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们提供你以不同的身份去旅行{\r}\N\NWe offer you a choice of alternate identities during your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想想看，干么以观光客的身份到火星去? 你可以花花公子的身份去{\r}\N\NI mean, face it. Why go to Mars as a tourist when you can go as a playboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是著名的运动员，或…{\r}\N\Nor a famous jock or--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“秘密情报员”{\r}\N\N''Secret agent.''
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这要多少钱？{\r}\N\NHow much is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我来对你详细解说一下，你是个第一流的情报员 乔装卧底执行你最重要的任务{\r}\N\NLet me tantalize you. You're a top operative, back under deep cover on your most important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黑白两道的人马都在追杀你{\r}\N\NPeople are trying to kill you, left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美丽的，富异国情调的女人{\r}\N\NYou meet this beautiful, exotic woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说下去{\r}\N\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想破坏你到时候享受的乐趣{\r}\N\NI don't wanna spoil it for you, Doug...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我向你保证，在旅程结束时{\r}\N\Nbut you wrest the shore, by the time the trip is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你将获得美人的芳心，杀光坏人 拯救整个星球！{\r}\N\Nyou get the girl, kill the bad guys and save the entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说说看{\r}\N\NNow, you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不值得花三百个信用单位吗?{\r}\N\NIsn't that worth a measly 300 credits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是你的第一次旅行？ - 嗯{\r}\N\N- It this your first trip? - Um-Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别担心，咱们这里很少会出差错的{\r}\N\NWell, don't worry. Things hardly ever fuck up around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安，道格{\r}\N\NGood evening... Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我是楼大夫 - 幸会{\r}\N\N- I'm Dr. Lull. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}厄尼，连结第62B及37号的细胞问质{\r}\N\NErnie, patch in matrix 62-B-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有，你想增加些外星怪物吗?{\r}\N\NAnd, would you like us to integrate some alien stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好啊，有何不可?{\r}\N\NSure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}双头怪物？{\r}\N\NTwo-headed monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你从来不看新闻吗？{\r}\N\NDon't you keep up with the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们现在研究外星人的史前古迹 - 看起来真古怪{\r}\N\N- We're doing alien artifacts now. - It's wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊，它们有数百万年的历史{\r}\N\NYeah, they date back a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 厄尼？ - 这玩意是新的{\r}\N\N- Ernie? - That's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}结婚很久了?{\r}\N\N- Blue sky on Mars. - Been married long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 八年了 - 噢，我明白了{\r}\N\N- Eight years. - Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}背着老婆出来找些刺激?{\r}\N\NSlipping away for a little hanky-panky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不完全是，我一直对火星感兴趣 - 系统运行{\r}\N\N- Not really. I've always been fascinated with Mars. - All systems go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以开始了{\r}\N\NNumber seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准备进入梦乡了？{\r}\N\NReady for dreamland?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先，我要问你几个问题 如此我们才能适当调整自我之旅{\r}\N\NI'll be asking you some questions, Doug, so we can fine-tune the Ego program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你若能老实回答 你的旅程就会更加偷快{\r}\N\NYou answer honestly, you'll enjoy yourself whole a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的性活动倾向是什么? - 异性{\r}\N\N- Your sexual orientation. - Hetero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，你喜欢什么样的女人?{\r}\N\NHow do you like your women?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}金发的？褐发的？红发的？{\r}\N\NBlonde? Brunette? Redhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}褐发的{\r}\N\NBrunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}苗条的运动员型？肉感型？{\r}\N\NSlim. Athletic. Voluptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}运动员型{\r}\N\NAthletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}端庄型？侵略型？轻佻型？{\r}\N\NDemure. Aggressive. Sleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老实回答{\r}\N\NBe honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}轻佻型…{\r}\N\NSleazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}端庄型…{\r}\N\NDemure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 41A，厄尼{\r}\N\N- 41A, Ernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天，他将度过一段狂野的时光？{\r}\N\NOh, boy, is he gonna have a wild time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他会不想回来？ - 这是一定的{\r}\N\N- Is he not gonna want to come back? - Oh, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么...{\r}\N\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说呢？{\r}\N\Nwhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我难以决定，连个纪念品也没有{\r}\N\NI'm not so sure, and I don't get a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也不尽然，你只要加些额外费用 我们就提供Ｔ恤，以及你在观光点拍的照片{\r}\N\NNot true. For just a few more credits, we supply T-shirts, snapshots of you at the site...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}甚至信件…{\r}\N\Nand even letters from the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么事？ - 你最好快来这边一下{\r}\N\N- What is it? - You'd better get down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我正在和一个重要客户谈生意{\r}\N\NLook, I am with a very important client.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看来咱们又碰上另一个精神分裂栓患者{\r}\N\NIt looks like we got another schizoid embolism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我马上回来{\r}\N\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麦克连先生?{\r}\N\NUh, Mr. McClane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鲍伯，出了什么事？{\r}\N\NBob! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别让她走掉！{\r}\N\NDon't let her leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们死定了！你们每一个！{\r}\N\NGet off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们暴露了我的身份！{\r}\N\NYou blew my cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你连个简单的植入手术都做不好{\r}\N\NYou can't do a simple goddamn double implant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是我的错，他的记忆有问题{\r}\N\NNot my fault. We hit a memory cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们随时会到 他们会杀了你们！{\r}\N\NThey'll be here at any minute! They'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他在说些什么？ - 放开我！{\r}\N\N- What is he talking about? - Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德先生，试着冷静下来！{\r}\N\NMr. Quaid, try to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的名字不叫魁德{\r}\N\NMy name is not Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 让我走，快替我松绑！ - 厄尼，抓住他的腿！{\r}\N\N- Let me go! Untie me now! - Ernie, grab his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 快拉住他！ - 放开我！{\r}\N\N- Hold him down! - Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没事吧？{\r}\N\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听我说 他一直不停地说着火星的事{\r}\N\NListen to me. he's been going on and on about Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他真的到过那里！ - 用你的脑袋想想，你这笨女人！{\r}\N\N- He has really been there. - Use your head, you dumb bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他刚刚的表现 正是自我旅行中的情报员角色！{\r}\N\NHe's just acting out the 'secret agent' portion of his ego trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这恐怕是不可能的 - 为什么？{\r}\N\N- I'm afraid that's not possible. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我们根本还没将记忆植入！{\r}\N\NBecause we haven't implanted it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}惨了，这下可惨了！{\r}\N\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这正是我要告诉你的 有人洗掉了他的记忆！{\r}\N\NI've been trying to tell you, someone has erased his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起{\r}\N\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是说“某人”？{\r}\N\N'Someone'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在谈论该死的情报机构{\r}\N\NWe're talking about the fucking Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 闭嘴！ - 鲍伯，那个客户走了{\r}\N\N- Shut up! - Bob, the client's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，好，听我说，咱们就这么办 我们将他所有关于瑞可的记忆通通洗掉{\r}\N\NOk, all right. Look, here's what we're gonna do. Renata, cover up any memory he's got of us or Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我尽力而为，他的记忆乱成一团{\r}\N\NI'll do what I can. It's pretty messy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}厄尼，把他搬下去送上出租车 蒂凡霓，你帮他{\r}\N\NErnie, dump him in a cab, around the corner. Tiffany, you help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要毁掉他的资料，退回他的钱{\r}\N\NI'm gonna destroy his file and refund his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果有人找上门来 就说我们从没听过道格?魁德{\r}\N\NAnd if anybody comes asking, we never even heard of Douglas Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在哪里？{\r}\N\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在一辆钱宁出租车上{\r}\N\NYou're in a Johnnycab.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是说，我怎么会在这里?{\r}\N\NI mean what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起 你能换个方式问这问题吗？{\r}\N\NI'm sorry. Would you please rephrase the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怎么会坐上这辆出租车？{\r}\N\NHow did I get in this taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}车门打开，你就上了车{\r}\N\NThe door opened, you got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}累了一天，是吧?{\r}\N\NHell of a day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这里可以吧？ - 停在这边{\r}\N\N- This okay? - Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 多谢你搭乘钱宁出租车 - 谢谢你{\r}\N\N- Thank you for taking Johnnycab. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望你满意我们的服务{\r}\N\NHope you enjoyed the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗨，魁德！{\r}\N\NHey, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哈利? - 你的火星之旅如何？{\r}\N\N- Harry. - How was your trip to Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么旅行？ - 你到瑞可公司去，还记得吧？{\r}\N\N- What trip? - You went to Rekall. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我有吗？ - 是的，你去了{\r}\N\N- I did? - Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我叫你别去，但你偏要去 - 你是谁？我爸爸？{\r}\N\N- I told you not to, but you went in anyway. - What are you, my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 来吧，我请你喝一杯 - 听着，我已晚到家了，谢谢你。不过...{\r}\N\N- Come on, I'll buy you a drink. - Listen. I'm already late, thank you very much. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，带上他...快点{\r}\N\NOkay, bring him-- come on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}咱们这就去喝一杯。快！{\r}\N\NLet's go get that drink. move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这到底是怎么回事？ 我到底做错了什么？{\r}\N\NWhat is going on? what the fuck did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 告诉我啊！ - 你乱说话！魁德，你乱说关于火星的事！{\r}\N\N- Tell me! - You blabbed, Quaid, you blabbed about Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你疯了吗？ 我对火星一无所知啊？{\r}\N\NAre you crazy? I don't even know anything about Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你该听我的话，魁德 我试着让你别惹上麻烦{\r}\N\NYou should've listened to me, Quaid. I was there to keep you out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈利，你这么做可就错了 你将我误认为某个人{\r}\N\NHey, you're making a big mistake. you got me mixed up with somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不对，兄弟 是你误认自己是某人{\r}\N\NUh-uh, pal. You got yourself mixed up with somebody--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抛，发球{\r}\N\NAnd pivot... and serve...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}收拍，抽球{\r}\N\Nand shift... and stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好，完美的动做{\r}\N\NVery good. perfect form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的{\r}\N\NHi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你在干什么? - 刚刚有几个人想杀我{\r}\N\N- What are you doing? - Some men just tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抢匪？你没事吧？{\r}\N\NMuggers? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，他们是间谍之类的{\r}\N\NNo, they were spies or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有我的同事哈利，他… 快蹲下！{\r}\N\NAnd Harry, from work, he was the-- get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我的同事哈利，他是带头大哥 - 冷静下来，道格，好吗?{\r}\N\N- Harry was the boss. - Take it easy, Doug, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 把事情的经过详细地告诉我。为何会有间谍想要杀你? - 我不知道{\r}\N\N- Tell me exactly what happened. Why would spies wanna kill you? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 但和火星有关 - 火星？你甚至没到过火星啊！{\r}\N\N- But it had something to do with Mars. - Mars? You haven't even been to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道这听来很荒唐 但我今天去了那瑞可公司…{\r}\N\NI know, it sounds crazy, but I went to this Rekall place after work--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你跑去找那些脑科杀手? - 先让我把话说完{\r}\N\N- You went to those brain butchers? - Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们把你怎么了？告诉我 - 我到火星旅游了一次。结果…{\r}\N\N- What did they do to you, tell me? - I got a trip to Mars. And.. so what happened was
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别管瑞可的事行不行？ 那些人想杀我啊！{\r}\N\NForget about Rekall, will you? These guys were going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 道格，没有人想杀你 - 他们想杀我{\r}\N\N- Doug, nobody tried to kill you. - They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我杀了他们！{\r}\N\NBut I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听我说，亲爱的… 那些瑞可的混蛋弄坏了你的脑袋{\r}\N\NListen to me, sweetheart. Those assholes at Rekall have fucked up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.29,0:24:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你开始产生偏执的幻想{\r}\N\NYou're having paranoid delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.60,0:24:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说这也是幻想吗？{\r}\N\NYou call this a delusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.73,0:24:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 道格，我要打电话叫医生来 - 不，别打电话给任何人！{\r}\N\N- Doug, I'm gonna call a doctor. - Don't. Don't call anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.03,0:25:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗莉，快走，离开这里！{\r}\N\NLori, go! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.85,0:26:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为什么要这么做？罗莉{\r}\N\NWhy are you doing this, Lori?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.10,0:26:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说！我叫你说！{\r}\N\NTalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.57,0:26:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不是你太太 - 你不是才怪{\r}\N\N- I'm not your wife. - The hell you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.71,0:26:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我发誓我六个礼拜以前没见过你{\r}\N\NI swear to God I never saw you before six weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.61,0:26:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们的婚姻只是植入的记忆{\r}\N\NOur marriage is just a memory implant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为我是个笨蛋？ 我记得我们的婚礼{\r}\N\NYou think I'm stupid? I remember our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.40,0:26:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是情报局植入的记忆{\r}\N\NIt was an implant by the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.57,0:26:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 恋爱？ - 植入的{\r}\N\N- Falling in love. - Implanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.37,0:26:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们的朋友？我的工作？八年在一起的时光？ 难道这些也全是植入的记忆?{\r}\N\NOur friends, my job, 8 years together. Suppose all of these was implanted, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.51,0:26:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}工作是真的 是情报局替你安排的{\r}\N\NThe job's real. The Agency set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:26:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}狗屁！{\r}\N\NBullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.18,0:27:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们抹掉你的身份 植入一个新的{\r}\N\NThey erased your identity and implanted a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.25,0:27:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我被安排来当你的太太 以便就近监视，确定你的记忆被彻底洗干净{\r}\N\NI was written in as your wife so that I could watch you and make sure the erasure took.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，魁德{\r}\N\NSorry, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.60,0:27:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这一生只是一场梦{\r}\N\NYour whole life is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，那么…如果我不是我… 那么我又是谁？{\r}\N\NOkay, then if I'm not me, who the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.77,0:27:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}问倒我了{\r}\N\NBeats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.18,0:27:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是奉命派来这里工作{\r}\N\NI just work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.59,0:27:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格，我要你知道一件事{\r}\N\NDoug, there's something I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.72,0:27:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是我出过的任务中最棒的 我是说真的{\r}\N\NYou were the best assignment I ever had. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.83,0:27:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我感到很荣幸{\r}\N\NI'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.40,0:27:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真的不要再来一次吗? 念夜往日的情份上…{\r}\N\NYou sure you don't want to, just for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.70,0:27:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧，如果你不信任我 可以把我绑起来{\r}\N\NCome on, if you don't trust me, you can tie me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.71,0:28:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不晓得你原来这么变态 - 或许你也该知道这点了{\r}\N\N- I didn't know you were so kinky. - Maybe it's time you found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.92,0:28:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好聪明的女孩{\r}\N\NClever girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.79,0:28:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你该不会真的开枪吧？道格 咱们毕竟夫妻一场啊！{\r}\N\NYou wouldn't shoot me, will you? Doug. after all we've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的，的确有些偷快的时光…{\r}\N\NSome of it was fun.
