Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.36,0:29:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他想起了什么？ - 到目前为止什么也没有{\r}\N\N- What does he remember? - Nothing, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.17,0:29:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我追踪到他了{\r}\N\NI've got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.35,0:29:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}糟糕，他朝地下铁的方向去了 咱们追上去 咱们走！{\r}\N\NShit! He's going for the subway. Let's get him. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}收拾行李离开这里{\r}\N\NPack your stuff and get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.04,0:29:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他们把他抓回来呢?{\r}\N\NWhat if they bring him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.04,0:29:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是不可能的{\r}\N\NNot a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.62,0:29:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}地下铁，快！{\r}\N\NSubway! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.73,0:30:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抓住他 他身上有枪！{\r}\N\NGet him! he's got a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.83,0:30:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 堵住他的去路，那边！ - 站住！别动！{\r}\N\N- Cut him off! That way! - Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.97,0:30:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.26,0:30:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}自动扶梯{\r}\N\NThe escalator.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.56,0:30:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们四个上去！你跟我来！{\r}\N\NYou four go up. you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.88,0:31:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}闪开！闪开！{\r}\N\NGet out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.21,0:31:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}闪开！闪开！{\r}\N\NGet out of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}站台！{\r}\N\NThe platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.62,0:31:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哪边？ - 右边！{\r}\N\N- Which way? - To the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}巴科，明日的燃料，明日的价格{\r}\N\NBotco. tomorrow's fuels, tomorrow's prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.74,0:32:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别满足于苍白的回忆 别被骗去植入假记忆{\r}\N\NDon't settle for pale memories. Don't go for fake implants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.08,0:32:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以传统方式享受一次美好的假期{\r}\N\NExperience space travel the old-fashioned way...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.48,0:32:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}人人享受得起！{\r}\N\Non a real, live holiday you can afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.02,0:32:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要那王八蛋死！{\r}\N\NI want that fucker dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能体会你的心情 我也不愿意让魁德这种人玩我的老婆{\r}\N\NI don't blame you, man. I wouldn't want a guy like Quaid porking my old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.10,0:32:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是说她喜欢这么做？ - 不，我认为她痛恨和他在一起的每一刻{\r}\N\N- You're saying she likes it? - No, I'm sure she hated every minute of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.03,0:32:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请接科海根先生的传真电话\N\NSix-beta-nine, we have a live transmission from Mr. Cohaagen. 6B9，6B9{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我是瑞克特，传过来 - 请讲，科海根先生{\r}\N\N- Richter here. Patch it through. - You're a go, Mr. Cohaagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.14,0:33:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这到底是怎么一回事？ - 我正在追杀一个叛徒，长官{\r}\N\N- What is the fuck is going on down there? - I'm trying to neutralize a traitor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.65,0:33:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我要他死，你这白痴 就不会将他丢在地球上！{\r}\N\NIf I wanted him dead, you moron. I would have done it on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.62,0:33:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不能让他到处跑 他知道太多的秘密{\r}\N\NWe can't let him run around. He knows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.22,0:33:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗莉说他什么也不记得{\r}\N\NLori says he can't remember jackshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.39,0:33:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在是如此 一小时后他将完全恢复记忆{\r}\N\NThat's an hour, an hour he could have total recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.06,0:33:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给我听着，瑞克特 我要你将魁德活着送回来，重新植入记忆{\r}\N\NListen to me, Richter. I want Quaid delivered alive for reimplantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.80,0:33:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听清楚了没？{\r}\N\NHave you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.23,0:33:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要他回去跟罗莉重聚{\r}\N\NI want him back in place with Lori.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.60,0:33:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听见了没?{\r}\N\NDid you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说什么?长官，我听不见{\r}\N\NWhat was that, sir? I couldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.71,0:33:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在干什么? 我追踪到梅琳娜{\r}\N\NWhat are you doing? I got Quaid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.81,0:33:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}转到另一个频道，长官 有太阳黑子干扰{\r}\N\NSwitching to another channel, sir. I've got sunspots.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.85,0:33:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 给我回电话！给我回电话！ - 我无法接收到你了{\r}\N\N- Call him back! - I'm losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.18,0:33:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他在哪？ - 加星利区，第二层{\r}\N\N- Where is he? - Second level, galleria.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你该在火星上就把魁德干掉的{\r}\N\NWe should've killed Quaid on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.62,0:34:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“丽池大饭店”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.75,0:34:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 信号的接收状况呢？ - 好极了{\r}\N\N- How are we doing? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.17,0:34:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在将它放大{\r}\N\NZooming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.08,0:34:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}锁定住他了！{\r}\N\NWe got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.70,0:34:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你想活命，就别挂断{\r}\N\NIf you want to live, don't hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.17,0:34:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你想怎样！ - 你身上有追踪器{\r}\N\N- What do you want? - I've got your bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.17,0:34:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在三分钟后就要破门而入 除非你照我的话去做{\r}\N\NThey'll be bust in your door in three minutes unless you do exactly as l say.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.51,0:34:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不必找了，追踪器在你的头里{\r}\N\NDon't bother searching. the bug's in your skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是谁？ - 别管我是谁{\r}\N\N- Who are you? - Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找条湿毛巾包在你的头上 这可以减弱讯号{\r}\N\NWet a towel and wrap it around your head. that'll muffle the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.35,0:34:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是如何找到我的？ - 我奉劝你最好快点照办{\r}\N\N- How'd you find me? - I'd advise you to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.16,0:35:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这可让你争取一些时间 他们将无法锁定你{\r}\N\NThis'll buy you some time. they won't be able to pinpoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.33,0:35:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 该死！ - 怎么回事？{\r}\N\N- Shit! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.97,0:35:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我追丢他了 - 再给我找！{\r}\N\N- I lost him. - Well, find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.61,0:35:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的{\r}\N\NYeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.24,0:35:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点，你看来很正点{\r}\N\NCome on, hurry up. You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.01,0:35:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在到窗口去 快去{\r}\N\NNow go to the window. go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.12,0:35:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看得见我吗？ - 嗯{\r}\N\N- Can you see me down here? - Um-hum.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.35,0:35:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是你交给我的那口箱子 - 我交给你的？{\r}\N\N- This is the suitcase you gave me. - I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我把它放在这里 你到下面来拿，然后继续走{\r}\N\NI'm gonna set it here. You come and get it, keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 慢着，等一下！ - 什么事?{\r}\N\N- Wait. Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.56,0:35:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是谁? - 我是你在火星情报局时的同事{\r}\N\N- Who are you? - We were buddies in the Agency back on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.23,0:35:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说过你若是失踪的话就来找你 所以我来了，再见{\r}\N\NYou asked me, if you disappeared, to come and find you, so here I am. Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.74,0:35:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在火星上时是做什么?{\r}\N\NWhat was I doing on Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.64,0:35:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，太太，这是我的{\r}\N\NExcuse me, Mam, but this is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.71,0:36:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 上面又没写你的名字！ - 是人家留给我的{\r}\N\N- I don't see your name on it. - Someone left it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.95,0:36:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 去找你自己的箱子！ - 对不起，太太，我真的需要它{\r}\N\N- Find your own bag. - Excuse me, Mam, but I need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.98,0:36:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}操你的，你这王八蛋！{\r}\N\NFuck you, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.22,0:36:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那狗娘养的一定就在这附近{\r}\N\NSon of a bitch's gotta be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.19,0:36:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那边那家伙！{\r}\N\NThat guy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.07,0:36:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈罗，我是钱宁出租车 今晚上哪去?{\r}\N\NHello, I'm Johnnycab. where can l take you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.21,0:36:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开车！开车！{\r}\N\NDrive. Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.38,0:36:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 麻烦你重复一下这地址好吗? - 上哪去都行，开车就是了！{\r}\N\N- Would you please repeat the destination? - Anywhere! Just go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.82,0:36:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请说出一个街名和号码{\r}\N\NPlease state the street and number.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈的！妈的！{\r}\N\NShit. Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.99,0:36:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没听过这个地址 能否请你重复…{\r}\N\NI'm not familiar with that address. would you please repeat--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.36,0:37:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}系上你的安全带{\r}\N\NFasten your seat belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.57,0:37:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}车资一共是18个信用单位{\r}\N\NThe fare is 18 credits, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去告我好了，笨蛋{\r}\N\NSue me, dickhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.01,0:37:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望你满意我们的服务！{\r}\N\NWe hope you enjoyed the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.63,0:39:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好，陌生人，我是豪瑟{\r}\N\NHowdy, stranger. this is Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.84,0:39:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果事情出了差错 我如今就得对着自己说话{\r}\N\NIf things have gone wrong, I'm talking to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.37,0:39:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你则得在头上包着湿毛巾{\r}\N\Nand you've got a wet towel wrapped around your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.71,0:39:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不管你叫什么名字 下面这事实包准叫你大吃一惊{\r}\N\NWhatever your name is, get ready for the big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.45,0:39:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你并不是你 你其实是我{\r}\N\NYou are not you. you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.58,0:39:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的?{\r}\N\NNo shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.19,0:39:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}6B9，6B9，请回答{\r}\N\NSix-beta-nine, six-beta-nine, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你找到他了?{\r}\N\NDid you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们扫瞄到废弃的水泥工厂 发生了一场爆炸{\r}\N\NWe picked up an explosion at the old cement factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.09,0:39:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 派两组人过去，咱们在那里碰头 - 知道了{\r}\N\N- Send two units. We'll meet you there. - Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.53,0:40:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我这辈子都在火星情报部工作{\r}\N\NAll my life I've worked for Mars Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.53,0:40:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}替科海根做了许多伤天害理的事{\r}\N\NI did Cohaagen's dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.43,0:40:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但几个礼拜前我遇到一个人，一个女人{\r}\N\NBut a few weeks ago I met somebody, a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.47,0:40:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她让我觉悟到一些事{\r}\N\NAnd I learned a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.67,0:40:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比方说，我是在助盗为虐{\r}\N\NLike, I've been playing for the wrong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.64,0:40:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在能做的 就是好好弥补一下过去的罪擎{\r}\N\NAll I can do now is try to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.38,0:40:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要知道，这个脑袋里装的东西 可以让科海根死得很惨{\r}\N\NSee, there's enough shit in here to fuck Cohaagen good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.98,0:40:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不幸的是，如果你听到这段话 就表示他已经先一步整倒了我{\r}\N\NUnfortunately, if you're listening to this, that means he has got to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.09,0:40:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最困难的部份就在此，兄弟{\r}\N\NAnd here comes the hard part, old buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.02,0:40:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从现在起全得靠你了{\r}\N\NNow it is all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.42,0:40:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真是太好了{\r}\N\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.24,0:40:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们找到了什么？ - 车上没有人{\r}\N\N- What have we got? - Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.47,0:40:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他已经走了 - 我抓到前方有微弱的讯号{\r}\N\N- He's gone. - I got a weak signal over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}散开，把他找出来{\r}\N\NSplit up. Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.51,0:40:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先，将你头里的追踪器取出来{\r}\N\NFirst let's get rid of that bug in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.55,0:40:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将这东西从箱子里拿出来 然接插进你的鼻子里{\r}\N\NTake this thing out of the case and stick it up your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.02,0:41:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别担心，它是自动导向的{\r}\N\NDon't worry. It's self-guiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.29,0:41:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}用力插进去就行了{\r}\N\NJust shove real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.30,0:41:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你听到一个碎裂声，那就是了{\r}\N\NWhen you hear a crunches, you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.70,0:41:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将它拉出来{\r}\N\NJust pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.40,0:41:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但得小心，那也是我的脑袋{\r}\N\NBe careful. It's my head too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.82,0:41:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我锁定住他了！{\r}\N\NI've got a lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.82,0:41:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在上面 咱们上！{\r}\N\NUp. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.53,0:41:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的计划是这样的…{\r}\N\NNow, this is the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.16,0:41:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你到火星上去{\r}\N\NGet your ass to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.59,0:41:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后到希尔顿饭店出示一份 布鲁贝克的证件给柜台接待员{\r}\N\Nthen go to the Hilton and flash the Brubaker I.D. at the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.30,0:41:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如此就行了{\r}\N\NThat's all does to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}照我的话去做，咱们两个就可以让那个狗杂种 得到应有的制裁。我全靠你了，兄弟{\r}\N\NJust do what I tell you. If we can nail this son of a bitch who fucked you and me.  I'm counting on you, Buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.24,0:42:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可别让我失望{\r}\N\NDon't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.01,0:42:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}正前方{\r}\N\NStraight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.08,0:42:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这里面{\r}\N\NIn there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.99,0:42:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那边{\r}\N\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.77,0:43:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给我！{\r}\N\NGive me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.18,0:43:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他妈的！{\r}\N\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.78,0:43:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上你妈的火星去... 上你妈的火星去...{\r}\N\NGet your ass to Mars-- get your ass to Mars--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.44,0:44:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎光临火星联邦自治区{\r}\N\NWelcome to the Mars Federal Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.11,0:44:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了各位的健康和舒适 我们建造了圆顶{\r}\N\NFor your safety and comfort, domes have been installed...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以隔绝外界的真空环境{\r}\N\Nto protect you from the vacuum outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.38,0:44:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请不要碰触外侧的窗户或气闸{\r}\N\NPlease do not touch exterior windows or air locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.15,0:44:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}由于本地的空气供应量极为有限 此地全面禁止吸烟…{\r}\N\NAnd since the air volume is limited. No smoking is allowed anywhere in the colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.96,0:44:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}下一个！{\r}\N\NNext.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.33,0:44:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢各位 祝你们在火星的停留期间偷快{\r}\N\NThank you, and enjoy your stay on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.36,0:44:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}护照呢?{\r}\N\NPassport.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.25,0:44:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 快点，闪一边去 - 让路！{\r}\N\N- Get out of the way. - Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.38,0:44:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}退后！{\r}\N\NStand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.29,0:44:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根先生要见你，马上！{\r}\N\NMr. Cohaagen wants to see you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.06,0:44:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有魁德的消息吗？{\r}\N\NAny news of Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.83,0:44:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 自从你追丢他之后就没有了 - 讲话当心点！上尉 - 我们有车送你到港口{\r}\N\N- Not since you lost him. - Watch your mouth, Captain. - We've got a car to take you from the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.83,0:44:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你打算在火星上停留多久？ - 两个礼拜{\r}\N\N- How long do you plan to stay? - Two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.24,0:45:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看那上面写的 “寡头万岁”{\r}\N\NLook at that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.47,0:45:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这他妈的又是什么？ - 火星的人民爱戴寡头{\r}\N\N- What the hell's this? - The Martians love Kuato.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.01,0:45:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们以为他是华盛顿再世{\r}\N\NThey think he's fuckin' George Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}宰了这混蛋{\r}\N\NKill the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.08,0:45:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没人知道他到底是谁{\r}\N\NNobody knows who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有携带任何水果或蔬菜吗?{\r}\N\NHave you brought any fruits  or vegetables onto the planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.55,0:45:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个礼拜{\r}\N\NTwo weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.75,0:45:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说什么？{\r}\N\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.26,0:45:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个礼拜{\r}\N\NTwo weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.26,0:45:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那不只是普通的涂鸦{\r}\N\NIt's not just graffiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.52,0:45:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叛军咋晚攻占了炼制厂{\r}\N\NThe rebels took over the refinery last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.96,0:45:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的Ｔ矿都无法输出{\r}\N\NNo terbinium is going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.76,0:45:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}情况还会更严重{\r}\N\NAnd it gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.35,0:45:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德{\r}\N\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.55,0:46:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那就是魁德！ - 哪里？{\r}\N\N- That's Quaid! - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.12,0:46:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个女人，把他抓起来！ 我是说“她”！{\r}\N\NThe woman! get him-- her!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.06,0:46:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}逮捕那女人！{\r}\N\NArrest that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.86,0:46:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抓住那女人！拦住她！{\r}\N\NGet that woman! Grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}接住！{\r}\N\NCatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.39,0:46:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准备大吃一惊吧！{\r}\N\NGet ready for a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.52,0:47:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 把这该死的门打开！ - 我办不到{\r}\N\N- Open the goddamn door! - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.56,0:47:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把它打开！{\r}\N\NOpen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.89,0:47:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些门和气闸是连接在一起的！{\r}\N\NThey're all connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.97,0:48:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 真可怕 - 而且前几天科海根又提高空气的价格{\r}\N\N- That's terrible. - And a few days ago Cohaagen raised the price of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.71,0:48:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 又一次？ - 地球上的人根本不管我们死活{\r}\N\N- Again? - Nobody on Earth gives a damn what happens up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.05,0:48:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们只要Ｔ矿 好能够去打他们那无聊的战争{\r}\N\NAnd they just want terbinium so they can fight the stupid war.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.02,0:48:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，那是什么？{\r}\N\NExcuse me. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.02,0:48:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是指那金字塔矿场？{\r}\N\NYou mean the Pyramid Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.19,0:48:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在那里工作过 直到他们在里面发现那些外星人留下来的东西{\r}\N\NI used to work there until they found that alien shit inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.92,0:48:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是传闻而已吗？{\r}\N\NWell, that's a rumor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.53,0:48:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为如此？{\r}\N\NThink so?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.62,0:49:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根先生{\r}\N\NMr. Cohaagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.36,0:49:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有事找我？长官{\r}\N\NYou wanted to see me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.96,0:49:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}瑞克特{\r}\N\NRichter...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.63,0:49:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道我为何如此快乐吗？{\r}\N\Ndo you know why I'm such a happy person?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.10,0:49:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道，长官{\r}\N\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.20,0:49:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我有全太阳系最棒的工作{\r}\N\NBecause I've got the greatest job in the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.57,0:49:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要Ｔ矿一直生产下去 我就能做任何我想做的事{\r}\N\NAs long as the terbinium keeps flowing, I can do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.71,0:49:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}任何事{\r}\N\NAnything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.61,0:49:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上…{\r}\N\NIn fact.,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.42,0:49:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我唯一担心的事只是 若有那么一天{\r}\N\NThe only thing I ever worried about is that one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.72,0:49:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叛军获得了胜利{\r}\N\Nif the rebels win...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.99,0:49:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一切就可能随之结束...{\r}\N\Nit all might end...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.69,0:49:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你却要造成这种结果！{\r}\N\Nand you're fucking making it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.96,0:49:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先你企图杀魁德 然后你又让他逃掉！{\r}\N\NFirst you trying kill Quaid, then you let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.10,0:49:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他有我们的人暗中帮助，长官{\r}\N\NHe had help from our side, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.80,0:49:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这我知道{\r}\N\NI know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.84,0:49:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 但我以为… - 谁叫你想？{\r}\N\N- But I thought-- - Who told you to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.54,0:49:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可没给你足够的数据来思考！{\r}\N\NI don't give you  enough information to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.08,0:50:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只要奉令行事就行了！{\r}\N\NYou do what you're told. that's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.92,0:50:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\N\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.66,0:50:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在…咱们开始来谈正事{\r}\N\NNow, let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.76,0:50:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们面临一个难缠的局面{\r}\N\NWe've got a tricky situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.43,0:50:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头要魁德脑袋里所知道的东西{\r}\N\NKuato wants what's in Quaid's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.06,0:50:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而且他也有可能得到 因为传闻他有心电感应的能力{\r}\N\NAnd he might be able to get it. cause they say he's psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.84,0:50:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而我已想出一个计划来阻止他成功{\r}\N\NAnd I have a plan to keep this from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.14,0:50:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为你这回可以好好合作吗?{\r}\N\NDo you think you could play along?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.14,0:50:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是的，长官 - 好极了{\r}\N\N- Yes, sir. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.48,0:50:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}否则，我就会取你的狗命！{\r}\N\NCause otherwise, I'll erase your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.90,0:51:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}出租车？你要坐出租车吗？ 先生，我的车上有杂志，音乐，威土忌{\r}\N\NTaxi? You need a taxi? Sir, I got magazines, music, whisky.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.19,0:51:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兄弟，要搭出租车吗？来吧{\r}\N\NYou need a cab, Man? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.55,0:51:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“希尔顿饭店”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.26,0:51:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}午安，我能效劳吗？{\r}\N\NAfternoon! Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.82,0:51:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的，麻烦你给我一个房间{\r}\N\NYes, I would like a room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.57,0:51:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎再次光临，布鲁贝克先生 你要同一间套房？{\r}\N\NNice to have you back, Mr. Brubaker. would you like the same suite?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.57,0:51:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然{\r}\N\NDefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.11,0:51:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你似乎有东西放在保管箱里{\r}\N\NSeemed you've left something in our safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.24,0:51:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}能否麻烦你将它拿来给我？{\r}\N\NCould you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.61,0:51:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要核对身份{\r}\N\NIdentification?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.39,0:52:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我这就去拿你房间的钥匙 - 谢谢{\r}\N\N- I'll go and code your room key. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.62,0:52:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“终极乐园”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.62,0:52:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“享受好时光，请找梅琳娜”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.71,0:52:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 钥匙在这里，布鲁贝克先生。西大楼的610号房 - 谢谢{\r}\N\N- There you go, Mr Brubaker. Suite 610 in the east wing. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.38,0:52:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我能借用你的笔吗? - 当然{\r}\N\N- Could I borrow your pen, please? - Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.86,0:52:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你{\r}\N\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.44,0:52:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兄弟，坐出租车？{\r}\N\NHey, man, you need a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.89,0:52:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这一辆的服务会比你差吗？ - 他可没有要养五个孩子啊！{\r}\N\N- What's wrong with this one? - He ain't got five kids to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.53,0:52:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的车在哪？ - 就在那边，兄弟{\r}\N\N- Where's yours? - Right over there, Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.37,0:53:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}王八蛋，这是我的客人啊！{\r}\N\NHey, asshole! that's my fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.21,0:53:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一边凉快去！{\r}\N\NEat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.58,0:53:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班尼，你这该死的…{\r}\N\NDamn you, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.22,0:53:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎光临火星，兄弟{\r}\N\NWelcome to Mars, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.86,0:53:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 刚刚那是什么？意外事件？ - 是反抗军干的{\r}\N\N- What the hell was that, an accident? - That's the rebels, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.56,0:53:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}咱们快离开此地吧！{\r}\N\NLet's get outta here...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.19,0:53:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}否则待会就会被捕{\r}\N\Nbefore they arrest us!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.16,0:53:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}反叛军要的是什么？{\r}\N\NWhat do the rebels want?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.26,0:53:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}和往常一样，更多的钱，更多自由，更多空气{\r}\N\NAll the usual. more money, more freedom, more air.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.47,0:53:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上哪去?{\r}\N\NSo, where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.77,0:53:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}终极乐园{\r}\N\NLast Resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.64,0:53:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}才刚到就迫不急待了？{\r}\N\NYou're getting off to an early start.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.65,0:53:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 第一回来火星？ - 是的{\r}\N\N- First time on Mars? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.91,0:53:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上…不是{\r}\N\NWell, actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.88,0:53:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也可说是{\r}\N\NWell, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.72,0:53:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天，连自己是否来过火星都弄不清楚{\r}\N\NDamn, the man don't even know whether he's been to Mars or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.23,0:54:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这就是了！维纳斯城{\r}\N\NVoila. Venusville.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.70,0:54:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看到中意的货色没？{\r}\N\NHey, you see anything you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.31,0:54:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}车子只能开到此 我们接下来最好用走的{\r}\N\NWell, this is the end of the line. we'd better walk from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.58,0:54:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我带你到那地方去{\r}\N\NI'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.58,0:54:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 想知道你的未来吗？ - 过去呢?{\r}\N\N- Do you wanna know the future? - What about the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.45,0:54:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧，就在转角的地方 就在这巷子里{\r}\N\NCome on, it's around the corner, right down this alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.29,0:54:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们这里什么都有{\r}\N\NThey got everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.73,0:54:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想爽一下吗？不错吧？{\r}\N\NNot bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.23,0:54:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看手相?读你的心思? 你的欲念？你心里的秘密？{\r}\N\NRead your palm? Your mind? Your aura? probe the secrets of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.73,0:54:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我打赌我猜得出你的生日 - 你说呢？{\r}\N\N- I bet I can guess your birthday. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.90,0:54:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是金牛座的，对吧 - 你怎么猜到的？{\r}\N\N- You're a Taurus, right? - How did you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.57,0:54:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 告诉我，所有的通灵人都是… - 变种？{\r}\N\N- Tell me something, are all the psychics-- - Freaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.94,0:54:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全是变种。是这一带的特产{\r}\N\NAfraid so. It goes with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.07,0:54:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们怎么会变成这样 - 廉价的圆顶，又没空气来挡有害的射线{\r}\N\N- What happened to them? - Cheap domes, and no air to clean up the rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.98,0:55:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，咱们到了，终极乐园 你真的要在这间玩吗？兄弟{\r}\N\NSo, this is it. The Last Resort. you sure you want to go in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.48,0:55:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有何不可？ - 我认识另外一家更好的{\r}\N\N- Why not? - I know this much better place down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.68,0:55:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}女孩子比较干净，酒也不掺水{\r}\N\NThe girls are cleaner, the liquor ain't watered down--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.69,0:55:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊，你还可以拿到回扣{\r}\N\NSure, and you get kickbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.99,0:55:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兄弟，我有五个孩子要养啊！{\r}\N\NHey, man, I got five kids to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.76,0:55:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}带他们去看牙医吧！{\r}\N\NTake them to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.96,0:55:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢了，先生，听我说，我在外面等你{\r}\N\NThanks, mister! Hey, mister, I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.30,0:55:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你慢慢玩好了 我叫班尼，班尼！{\r}\N\NTake your time. Benny's the name. Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.82,0:55:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要什么？ - 我找梅琳娜{\r}\N\N- What do you want? - I'm looking for Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.95,0:55:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她现在很忙{\r}\N\NShe's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.66,0:55:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找马丽好了，她有空(免费){\r}\N\NBut Mary here, she's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.69,0:55:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是免费，亲爱的，而是…{\r}\N\NWell, not free, honey, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.06,0:55:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有空{\r}\N\Navailable. Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.57,0:55:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢，我还是等梅琳娜好了{\r}\N\NThanks. I'll wait for Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.97,0:55:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}地球无赖！{\r}\N\NEarth slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.37,0:56:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}问题是，梅琳娜对客人是很挑的{\r}\N\NThing is, friend, mel's real picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.84,0:56:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她一向只招待熟客人{\r}\N\NShe kinds sticks to her regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.38,0:56:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她会喜欢我的{\r}\N\NShe'll like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.44,0:56:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅琳娜！{\r}\N\NMel! Hey, Mel!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.51,0:56:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈罗，豪瑟{\r}\N\NHello, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.81,0:56:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看得出你仍是全身鼓胀如昔{\r}\N\NStill bulging, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.15,0:56:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 近来都喂养什么? - 金发女郎{\r}\N\N- What have you been feeding this thing? - Blondes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.78,0:56:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我想它八成没吃饱了？{\r}\N\NI think it's still hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.02,0:57:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还有脸跑来这里啊？豪瑟{\r}\N\NYou got a lot of nerve showing your face around here, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.33,0:57:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这句话应该是我说的才对{\r}\N\NLook who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.43,0:57:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}东尼，别再烦他了{\r}\N\NHey, Tony, give the big guy a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.13,0:57:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放轻松点，如此才活得久{\r}\N\NRelax. You'll live longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.83,0:57:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧！{\r}\N\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.28,0:57:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 亲爱的，替我去招待东尼好吗？ - 没问题{\r}\N\N- Honey, take care of Tony, will you? - No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.21,0:57:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你应付不了这一个 就喊我一声{\r}\N\NIf you need any help with this one, give me a holler.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.30,0:57:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这狗娘养的！{\r}\N\NYou son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.03,0:57:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还活着？ 我都以为你被科海根折磨死了{\r}\N\NYou're alive? I thought that Cohaagen tortured you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.14,0:57:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想他大概没这么做吧{\r}\N\NWell, I guess he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.97,0:57:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你却无法传个口信给我？ 你难道都没关心过我的死活?{\r}\N\NAnd you couldn't get me a message? You never even wondered what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.25,0:58:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}豪瑟，谢天谢地，你还活着{\r}\N\NHauser! Hauser, thank God you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.49,0:58:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅琳…梅琳娜 梅琳娜，梅琳娜！{\r}\N\NMelin-- Melina. Melina.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.76,0:58:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我有话要告诉你 - 什么事？{\r}\N\N- I have to tell you something. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.76,0:58:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我已经不记得你了 - 你在胡说些什么？{\r}\N\N- I don't remember you. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.50,0:58:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不记得你了{\r}\N\NI don't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.70,0:58:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不记得我们之间的事 我甚至不记得我自己的过去{\r}\N\NI don't remember us. I don't even remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.81,0:58:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么？你得了失忆症？ 你是如何找来这里的？{\r}\N\NOh, what? Did you get amnesia? how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.47,0:58:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 豪瑟留给我一张字条 - 豪瑟？你就是豪瑟{\r}\N\N- Hauser left me a note. - You're Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.04,0:58:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}已经不是了{\r}\N\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.05,0:58:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在是魁德 道格拉斯?魁德{\r}\N\NNow I'm Quaid. Douglas Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.48,0:58:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 豪瑟，你精神错乱了 - 我没有精神错乱。科海根偷了我的记忆{\r}\N\N- Hauser, you've lost your mind. - I didn't lose my mind. Cohaagen stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.35,0:58:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他发现豪瑟企图背叛他 于是将他变成另一个人，变成我{\r}\N\NHe found out that Hauser switched sides, so he turned him into somebody else: me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.15,0:58:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这故事太玄了{\r}\N\NThis is too weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.75,0:58:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再把我丢在地球上 给我一个老婆和一份烂工作{\r}\N\NHe dumped me on earth with a wife and a lousy job--
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.49,0:58:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说你有老婆？ 你他妈的结婚了？{\r}\N\NDid you say... Did you say wife? are you fucking married?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.53,0:58:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她其实不是我真正的太太 - 她不是你真正的太太？{\r}\N\N- She wasn't really my wife. - Oh, she isn't really your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.56,0:58:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可真笨 她是豪瑟的太太？{\r}\N\NHow stupid of me. she was Hauser's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 听着，忘了我提到… - 不，一切都别再说了！{\r}\N\N- Look, forget that I said wife. - No, let's just forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.97,0:59:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我受够了你和你那些谎言 - 我为何要骗你？{\r}\N\N- I'm sick of hearing your goddamn lies. - Why would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.80,0:59:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为你仍在为科海根工作{\r}\N\NBecause you're still working for Cohaagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.37,0:59:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别胡说了{\r}\N\NDon't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.55,0:59:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你根本就没爱过我，豪瑟{\r}\N\NYou never loved me, Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.81,0:59:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只想利用我，好混进去{\r}\N\NYou just used me to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.85,0:59:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}混进什么里面{\r}\N\NInside what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.86,0:59:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看你还是走吧{\r}\N\NI think you'd better leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.82,0:59:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 梅琳娜，豪瑟派我来做某件事 - 我可不会上当{\r}\N\N- Melina, Hauser sent me to do something. - I'm not falling for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.43,0:59:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说这脑袋里装的东西足以整垮科海根{\r}\N\NHe says there's enough in here to nail Cohaagen for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.43,0:59:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 滚！ - 你得帮我恢复记忆！{\r}\N\N- Get out! - You've got to help me remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.50,0:59:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我叫你滚！ - 梅琳娜，求求你{\r}\N\N- I said, get out! - Melina, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.80,0:59:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有人要杀我啊！{\r}\N\NPeople are trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.64,0:59:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的？{\r}\N\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.64,0:59:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，我这就走{\r}\N\NAll right, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.79,0:59:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}宝贝，你让我恨不得能有三只手{\r}\N\NBaby, you make me wish I had three hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.79,0:59:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你这两只手已经很够用了{\r}\N\NWell, I think you're doing just fine with two.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.63,1:00:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}失陪一下，宝贝，咱们待会再聊{\r}\N\NExcuse me, baby. we'll pick this up later.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.03,1:00:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兄弟，你不怎么持久啊！{\r}\N\NHey, that didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.63,1:00:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，我问你，你玩过变种妞吗？{\r}\N\NListen, let me ask you a question. did you ever fuck a mutant?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.17,1:00:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 送我回饭店去 - 我认识一对变种双胞胎{\r}\N\N- Take me to the hotel. - I know these Siamese twins.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.81,1:00:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}保证让你爽歪歪{\r}\N\NMan, you won't know if you're coming or going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.97,1:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天下午四点半时 我签署一份法令{\r}\N\NThis afternoon at 4:30 p.m., I signed an order declaring martial law...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.84,1:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}批准在火星联邦自治区实施戒严{\r}\N\Nthroughout the Mars Federal Colony.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.35,1:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我将不会再容忍任何 破坏矿物输出的行为{\r}\N\NI will not tolerate any further damage to our mineral export operations.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.92,1:00:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头先生和他手下的恐怖份子 必须明白一件事{\r}\N\NMr. Kuato and his terrorists must understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.32,1:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们这种自取毁灭的行为 只会为人民带来苦难和痛苦…{\r}\N\Nthat their self-defeating efforts will only bring misery and suffering to the people...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.16,1:00:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德先生？{\r}\N\NMr. Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.36,1:00:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\N\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.63,1:00:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要跟你谈谈 是关于豪瑟先生的事{\r}\N\NI need to talk to you about Mr. Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.10,1:00:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是谁？ - 瑞可公司的艾吉马大夫{\r}\N\N- Who are you? - Dr. Edgemar from Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.50,1:00:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是如何找到我的？ - 解释起来有点复杂{\r}\N\N- How did you find me? - It's a little difficult to explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.94,1:00:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能开门吗？ 我没有带武器{\r}\N\NCould you open the door? I'm unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.58,1:01:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别担心，我是一个人来的 我可以进去吗？{\r}\N\NDon't worry. I'm alone. may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.65,1:01:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你来做什么？ - 你听了后可能会有点难以接受{\r}\N\N- What do you want? - This is gonna be very difficult for you to accept, Mr Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.69,1:01:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我在听 - 你此时恐怕不是真的站在这里{\r}\N\N- I'm listening. - I'm afraid you're not really standing here right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.12,1:01:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你知道吗？大夫，你差点就骗过我了 - 我可是说正经的{\r}\N\N- Hum. You know. Doc, you could fool me. - I'm quite serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.53,1:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不在这里 我也不在{\r}\N\NYou're not here and neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.80,1:01:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这倒新鲜{\r}\N\NThat's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.10,1:01:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们又是在哪？ - 在瑞可公司{\r}\N\N- Where are we? - At Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.40,1:01:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你被绑在一张手术椅上{\r}\N\NYou're strapped into an implant chair...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.40,1:01:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而我则透过精神追踪探针 观察你的情形{\r}\N\Nand I'm monitoring you from the psychoprobe console.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.41,1:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白了，原来我是在做梦{\r}\N\NAh, I get it. I'm dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.68,1:01:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而这一切全是贵公司卖给我的 一回刺激的假期的一部份{\r}\N\NAnd all this is a part of the delightful vacation your company has sold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.48,1:01:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不完全是{\r}\N\NNot exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.88,1:01:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你目前所经历的，全是根据我们制作的记忆母带 所自由创造出来的幻象{\r}\N\NWhat you're experiencing is a free-form delusion based on our memory tapes...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.09,1:01:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你将不断地发展出新的情节{\r}\N\Nbut you're inventing it yourself as you go along.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.96,1:01:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}假设这是我创造出来的幻象 那么又是谁请你来插花的？{\r}\N\NWell, if it is my delusion, who the hell invited you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.49,1:01:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我被植入这程序 以便发生状况时能加以补救{\r}\N\NI've been artificially implanted as an emergency measure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.50,1:01:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不得不告诉你，魁德先生 你在手术中出现精神分裂栓{\r}\N\NI'm sorry to tell you this, Mr Quaid, but you've suffered a schizoid embolism.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.77,1:01:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们无法让你从幻想中醒来{\r}\N\NWe can't snap you out of your fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.57,1:02:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}于是我被派来 看看是否能劝你回到现实世界{\r}\N\Nand I've been sent in to try to talk you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.71,1:02:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根付你多少钱来干这种事？{\r}\N\NHow much is Cohaagen paying you for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.84,1:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想想看 你的梦是在植入的过程中开始的{\r}\N\NThink about it. Your dream started in the middle of the implant procedure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.08,1:02:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那以后发生的一切，包括追杀，到达火星{\r}\N\NEverything after that-- the chases, the trip to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.81,1:02:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}住宿于希尔顿饭店， 全是瑞可公司提供你的自我旅行情节{\r}\N\Nthe suite at the Hilton are all elements of your Rekall Holiday and Ego Trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.48,1:02:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你付钱来扮演秘密情报员{\r}\N\NYou paid to be a secret agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.81,1:02:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}狗屁，这不过是巧合罢了{\r}\N\NBullshit. It's coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.45,1:02:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么那个女孩呢？{\r}\N\NAnd what about the girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.99,1:02:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}褐发，运动员体型…既放荡又端庄？{\r}\N\NBrunette, athletic, sleazy and demure?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.89,1:02:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}完全符合你所指定的特征 这也是巧合吗？{\r}\N\NJust as you specified. Is that coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.56,1:02:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她是真的存在的 我在去瑞可之前就梦见过她了{\r}\N\NUh. She's real. l dreamt about her before I even went to Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.16,1:02:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德先生…{\r}\N\NMr. Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.46,1:02:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道你这逻辑有多荒唐吗？ 你梦见过她，所以她是真的？{\r}\N\NCan you hear yourself? she's real because you dreamed her?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.57,1:02:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没错 - 或许这将能使你信服…{\r}\N\N- That's right. - Oh, maybe this'll convince you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.67,1:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能把门打开吗？{\r}\N\NWould you mind opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.78,1:02:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你去开 - 没有必要动粗{\r}\N\N- You open it. - No need to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.58,1:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来开好了{\r}\N\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.92,1:02:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的？{\r}\N\NSweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.79,1:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进来吧，魁德太太{\r}\N\NCome in, Mrs. Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.00,1:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我猜你此时也不是真的在此了？ - 我在这里...{\r}\N\N- What I supposed you're not here either. - I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.07,1:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在瑞可公司{\r}\N\Nat Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.51,1:03:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我爱你{\r}\N\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.14,1:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊。所以你才会想杀我{\r}\N\NRight. That's why you tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.68,1:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我绝不会做任何伤害你的事{\r}\N\NNo. I'd never do anything to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.78,1:03:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要你回到我的身边{\r}\N\NI want you to come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.79,1:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 狗屁！ - 什么才是狗屁？魁德先生{\r}\N\N- Bullshit. - What's bullshit, Mr. Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.02,1:03:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是你的细胞受到精神化学损伤 而引发一连串偏执的幻想？{\r}\N\NThat you're having a paranoid episode triggered by acute neurochemical trauma?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.59,1:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还是你真的是一个 来自火星的卧底秘密情报员...{\r}\N\NOr that you're really an invincible secret agent from Mars...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.86,1:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}受到一项星际阴谋的迫害 让你自以为是个...{\r}\N\Nwho's the victim of an interplanetary conspiracy to make him think...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.10,1:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}卑微的建筑工人？{\r}\N\Nhe's a lowly construction worker?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.75,1:03:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别再折磨你自己了，道格{\r}\N\NStop punishing yourself, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.25,1:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是个正直的好人 你有个深爱着你的美丽妻子{\r}\N\NYou're a fine, upstanding man. you have a beautiful wife who loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.64,1:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还有许多美好的日子要过{\r}\N\NYour whole life is ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.58,1:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你得先愿意回到现实的世界{\r}\N\NBut you've got to want to return to reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.52,1:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就算我愿意好了…我又该怎么做？{\r}\N\NLet's assume I do, Then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.06,1:04:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 把这个吞下去 - 这是什么？{\r}\N\N- Swallow this. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.19,1:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它是一个象征 表示你愿意回到现实的世界{\r}\N\NIt's a symbol of your desire to return to reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.13,1:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在你的梦里，你将睡着{\r}\N\NInside your dream, you'll fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.47,1:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，假设你说的全是事实 这一切全是一场梦{\r}\N\NAll right, let's say you're telling the truth and this is all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.67,1:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我大可扣下扳机，反正也不要紧{\r}\N\NThen I could pull this trigger and it won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.48,1:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 道格，别这么做 - 这对我不会有什么差别，道格{\r}\N\N- Doug, don't. - It won't make a slightest difference to me, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.61,1:04:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但对你却会有毁灭性的结果 在你的脑海里，我将丧命{\r}\N\NBut the consequences to you would be devastating. In your mind I'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.25,1:04:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在无人引导你走出的情况下 你将陷入永久的精神错乱{\r}\N\NWith no one to guide you out, you'll be stuck in permanent psychosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.69,1:04:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格，让艾吉马大夫帮助你{\r}\N\NDoug, let Dr. Edgemar help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.12,1:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现实世界的墙将整个倒塌{\r}\N\NThe walls of reality will come crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.42,1:05:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在前一分钟里，你还是拯救叛军的大英雄 但接下来…你又将是科海根的心腹爪牙！{\r}\N\NOne minute, you will be hero who saved rebel clause. And the next thing you konw,  you'll be Cohaagen's bosom buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.37,1:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你甚至将如你当初所要求的 幻想在太空中发现外星文明{\r}\N\NYou'll even have fantasies about alien civilizations, as you requested...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.17,1:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但在你终于回到现实世界后 你将被切除前脑！{\r}\N\Nbut in the end, back on earth you'll be lobotomized!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.27,1:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以还是理智点，道格，把枪放下！{\r}\N\NSo get a grip on yourself, Doug, and put down that gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.08,1:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好。现在把那粒胶囊放进嘴里{\r}\N\NGood. Now take the pill and put it in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.09,1:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吞下去！{\r}\N\NSwallow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.66,1:05:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吞下去！亲爱的{\r}\N\NGo ahead, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.71,1:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看你干了什么好事！ 看你干了什么好事！{\r}\N\NNow you've done it. Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.17,1:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是回敬你害我跑来火星{\r}\N\NThat's for making me come to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.81,1:06:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道我有多痛恨这个烂星球！{\r}\N\NYou know how much I hate this fucking planet!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.28,1:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把他铐起来{\r}\N\NCuff him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.19,1:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我抓住他了 - 好极了，用服务电梯将他送下来{\r}\N\N- I got him. - Good. Bring him down in the service elevator.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.76,1:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们走{\r}\N\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.39,1:08:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}操你的！{\r}\N\NFuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.77,1:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}道格{\r}\N\NDoug.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.67,1:08:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的{\r}\N\NHoney...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.77,1:08:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不会伤害我，对不对？亲爱的{\r}\N\Nyou wouldn't hurt me, would you, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.18,1:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的…理智点{\r}\N\NSweetheart, be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.48,1:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}毕竟…咱们是夫妻啊！{\r}\N\NAfter all, we're married.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.22,1:08:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在离婚了{\r}\N\NConsider that a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.96,1:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她就是你的老婆？{\r}\N\NThat was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.70,1:08:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好一个贱人！{\r}\N\NWhat a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.11,1:08:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}闪一边去！{\r}\N\NHey, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.55,1:08:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还以为你不喜欢我{\r}\N\NI thought you didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.48,1:09:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果科海根要杀你，你就应该没问题{\r}\N\NIf Cohaagen wants you dead, you might be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.32,1:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 找到了 - 那么你是回来向我道歉了？{\r}\N\N- Got it. - So you've come back to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.82,1:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头要见你{\r}\N\NKuato wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.73,1:09:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快走！{\r}\N\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.59,1:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 现在怎么办？ - 跳！{\r}\N\N- Now what? - Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.88,1:10:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不！别开枪！ 你会把圆顶打破的！{\r}\N\NNo! Don't do it! you'll crack the fucking dome!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.38,1:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你这么做，咱们全都会没命 圆顶会破裂的！{\r}\N\NWhat are you trying to do, kill us? The dome will crack!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.73,1:10:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开！{\r}\N\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.90,1:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}出租车！{\r}\N\NTaxi!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.74,1:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅琳娜！梅琳娜！{\r}\N\NMelina! Melina!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.64,1:10:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要坐车吗？ - 快，到终极乐园{\r}\N\N- Need a ride? - Last Resort, quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.51,1:10:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们这些人尽在兜圈子{\r}\N\NYou guys are going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.99,1:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的天！{\r}\N\NJesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.05,1:10:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点！你开车！{\r}\N\NCome on! You drive!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.49,1:10:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们是惹上了什么麻烦？{\r}\N\NYou guys are in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.66,1:10:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开车！开车！{\r}\N\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.14,1:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是想害死我？兄弟 - 闭嘴，开你的车就行了！{\r}\N\N- What are you trying to do to me, Man? - Shut up and drive!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.14,1:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还有五个孩子要养啊！{\r}\N\NHey, I got five kids to feed!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.50,1:11:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}糟了！{\r}\N\NShit!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.73,1:11:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}车失灵了！{\r}\N\NNo brakes!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.67,1:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个白痴！{\r}\N\NYou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.54,1:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在干什么啊？{\r}\N\NWhat the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.02,1:12:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的天，现在他们也要杀我了！{\r}\N\NChrist! Now they're after me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.09,1:12:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把枪给我{\r}\N\NGive me that!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.89,1:12:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}滚一边去！{\r}\N\NGet out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.23,1:12:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}东尼！{\r}\N\NTony!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.21,1:12:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别挡路！ 快来！{\r}\N\NGet out of the way! come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.78,1:12:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快！快！{\r}\N\NCome on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.65,1:12:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，东尼{\r}\N\NThank you, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.01,1:13:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要…乐一下吗？{\r}\N\NHey, you wanna, have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.21,1:13:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在哪里？{\r}\N\NWhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.41,1:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在说什么啊？我不知道{\r}\N\NWhat are you talking about? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.82,1:13:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许你知道{\r}\N\NMaybe you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.95,1:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把他们都宰了！{\r}\N\NKill them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.80,1:13:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑卜琳娜！{\r}\N\NThumbelina!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.10,1:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}瑞克特！{\r}\N\NRichter!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.56,1:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 科海根打电话找你 - 我是瑞克特{\r}\N\N- A call from Cohaagen! - Richter here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.73,1:14:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们压制住他们了 - 停止战斗，将人员撤出{\r}\N\N- We've got them pinned down. - Stop fighting and pull out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.07,1:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但他们藏匿魁德，还保护他{\r}\N\NBut they've got Quaid. they're protecting him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.11,1:14:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好极了 立刻撤出G区{\r}\N\NPerfect. get out of Sector G now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.54,1:14:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别想{\r}\N\NDon't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.08,1:14:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 照办就是了！ - 是，长官{\r}\N\N- Do it! - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.95,1:14:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将人员撤回！{\r}\N\NPull'em out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.75,1:14:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有人员撤退！{\r}\N\NEverybody, pull out!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.09,1:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快！{\r}\N\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.80,1:14:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 科海根要将这一区封死！ - 快来！班尼{\r}\N\N- Cohaagen's sealing off the area! - Come on, Benny!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.65,1:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第一代的移民埋骨于此{\r}\N\NThe first settlers are buried here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.65,1:15:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们苦干到死 但财富却全落到科海根手里{\r}\N\NThey worked themselves to death, but cohaagen ended up with all the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.69,1:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他替他们建廉价的圆顶 让他们的后代变成奇形人{\r}\N\NHe built cheap domes and watched the kids turn into freaks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.59,1:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我见过他们了{\r}\N\NI saw them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.09,1:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你想呼吸，还得跟他买空气{\r}\N\NAnd if you want to breathe, you have to buy his air.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.76,1:15:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许你能改变这一切{\r}\N\NMaybe you can change all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.47,1:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我的爷爷可能也埋在这里{\r}\N\NHey, I think my grandpa might be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.74,1:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能做什么？{\r}\N\NSo what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.30,1:16:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头将让你想起 当你还是豪瑟时所知道的事{\r}\N\NKuato's gonna make you remember some things you knew when you were Hauser.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.01,1:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 比方说什么？ - 各种的事{\r}\N\N- Like what? - All sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.11,1:16:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 比方说，或许你会想起你曾爱过我 - 这倒不需要寡头的帮忙{\r}\N\N- Like maybe you'll remember you loved me. - I don't need Kuato for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.35,1:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从什么时候开始的？{\r}\N\NSince when?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.16,1:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别动！{\r}\N\NFreeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.16,1:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧，梅琳娜{\r}\N\NCome on, Melina.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.66,1:16:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头在等了{\r}\N\NKuato's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.27,1:16:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我找不到我的爷爷，但是...{\r}\N\NHey, I didn't find Grandpa, but--
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.74,1:16:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的妈呀！{\r}\N\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.34,1:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这家伙是谁？ - 是他帮助我们逃走的{\r}\N\N- Who's this? - He helped us get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.54,1:16:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们无须担心我，兄弟 我是站在你们这边的{\r}\N\NHey, don't worry about me, man. I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.42,1:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原来你是个变种人，是吧?{\r}\N\NYou're a mutant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.42,1:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧，我们走{\r}\N\NAll right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.56,1:17:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你有试过将门炸开吗？ - 你在这里等。跟我来{\r}\N\N- Have you tried ramming down the door? - You wait here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.70,1:17:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这么做也是没用的{\r}\N\NIt won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.70,1:17:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 科海根已经将通道减压 - 那就打通往M区的路{\r}\N\N- Cohaagen depressurized the tunnels. - Then drill through to Section M.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.21,1:17:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们办不到 空气已快耗尽了{\r}\N\NWe can't. we're running out of air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.24,1:17:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们需要援助{\r}\N\NWe need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.08,1:17:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，再忍耐一下 梅琳娜刚刚带着魁德到达此地{\r}\N\NOkay, sit tight. melina just got here with Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.12,1:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望他值得我们如此牺牲{\r}\N\NI hope he was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.82,1:17:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也是{\r}\N\NSo do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.85,1:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很高兴你们能及时赶来 - 你看来不怎么高兴{\r}\N\N- I'm glad you made it. - You don't look glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.86,1:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根封了维纳斯城。还停止供应空气{\r}\N\NCohaagen sealed up Venusville. he shut off the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.29,1:17:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你一定是知道某些重要的秘密，魁德{\r}\N\NYou must know something pretty damn important, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.60,1:17:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他要你{\r}\N\NHe wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.40,1:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我们不把你交出去 到了明早这一区的人都将没命{\r}\N\NIf we don't hand you over, everybody in this sector will be dead by morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.53,1:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么咱们也没什么选择的余地了{\r}\N\NThen we don't have much choice, do we.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.30,1:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不能把他交出去{\r}\N\NWe can't turn him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.84,1:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这得让寡头来决定 跟我来吧！魁德{\r}\N\NThat's up to Kuato. come with me, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.72,1:18:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐{\r}\N\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.72,1:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 寡头在哪？ - 在赶来此地的途中{\r}\N\N- Where's Kuato? - On his way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.66,1:18:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听过关于金字塔矿场的传闻吧？{\r}\N\NYou heard the rumors about the Pyramid Mine?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.36,1:18:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的{\r}\N\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.10,1:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根在那里面发现了某样东西 让他吓得要命{\r}\N\NCohaagen found something weird inside and it's got him scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.64,1:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么东西？外星人？{\r}\N\NWhat? Aliens?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.37,1:18:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你说呢？ - 我不知道{\r}\N\N- You tell me. - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.44,1:18:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的，你知道 所以我们才把你弄来这里{\r}\N\NYes, you do. that's why we brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.14,1:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根的大秘密...{\r}\N\NCohaagen's big secret is buried in that black hole...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.71,1:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}埋在你的脑里{\r}\N\Nyou call a brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.39,1:18:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头将要把它掘出来{\r}\N\NAnd Kuato's gonna dig it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.42,1:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你就是寡头，对吧？ - 错了{\r}\N\N- You're Kuato, right? - Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.62,1:18:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寡头是个变种人 当你见到他时可别大惊小怪{\r}\N\NKuato's a mutant, so don't get upset when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.46,1:19:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想要什么？魁德先生{\r}\N\NWhat do you want, Mr. Quaid?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.53,1:19:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}和你要的一样，恢复记忆{\r}\N\NSame as you: to remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.53,1:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但，又是为了什么？{\r}\N\NBut why?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.36,1:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 为了能再成为我自己 - 你的所做所为决定你是什么人{\r}\N\N- To be myself again. - You are what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.74,1:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}个人的价值端视他的所做所为{\r}\N\NA man is defined by his actions...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.41,1:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而不是他的记忆{\r}\N\Nnot his memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.68,1:19:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来请...{\r}\N\NPlease...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.98,1:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}握住我的双手{\r}\N\Ntake my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.39,1:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在，对我敞开你的心灵{\r}\N\NNow open your mind to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.96,1:20:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜托{\r}\N\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.26,1:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敞开你的心灵…{\r}\N\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.20,1:20:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敞开你的心灵…{\r}\N\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.74,1:20:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敞开你的心灵…{\r}\N\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.94,1:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敞开你的心灵…{\r}\N\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.55,1:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敞开你的心灵…{\r}\N\NOpen your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.04,1:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们得在叛军启动它之前毁掉它{\r}\N\NWe should blow the thing up before the rebels turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.44,1:21:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为咱们可试着将它启动 看看会有何结果{\r}\N\NI say we throw the switch and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.18,1:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别傻了！ - 我们不能冒这种险{\r}\N\N- Don't be an idiot. - We can't risk it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.28,1:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}引发的连锁反应 可能会毁掉这星球上所有的Ｔ矿{\r}\N\NThe chain reaction could spread to all the terbinium in the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.08,1:21:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也就是熔毁 整个星球都可能会熔毁{\r}\N\NThat means a meltdown, a meltdown on a planetary scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.05,1:21:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想造这玩意的人没想到这点?{\r}\N\NDon't you think whoever built this thing thought of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.55,1:21:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁晓得它们是怎么想的? 它们又不是人类{\r}\N\NWho knows what the hell they thought? they weren't human.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.96,1:21:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许这是个陷井 或许它们就是要让这星球熔毁{\r}\N\NMaybe it's a trap. maybe they want a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.56,1:21:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们甚至不知道这是否还能用{\r}\N\NWe don't even know if this piece of junk will work.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.96,1:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它的历史有多久？一百万年？五十万年？{\r}\N\NWhat is it? a million? Half a million?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.10,1:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 约有五十万年 - 是五十万年前造的{\r}\N\N- About half a million. - Half a million years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.80,1:21:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只需不让寡头…{\r}\N\NLet's make sure Kuato--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.10,1:22:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}醒醒！醒醒！ 快点！醒过来啊！{\r}\N\NWake up! Wake up! come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.34,1:22:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们找到我们了！该死！ 我们走吧！{\r}\N\NThey found us! Shit! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.18,1:22:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快醒醒，清醒过来，快！{\r}\N\NWake up! Snap out of it! Now! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.02,1:22:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们杀进来了{\r}\N\NThey found us!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.39,1:22:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 大伙儿撤退！ - 梅琳娜！{\r}\N\N- Everybody out! - Melina!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.05,1:22:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快走！走啊！{\r}\N\NGet moving! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.92,1:22:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走啊！{\r}\N\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.10,1:22:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大伙儿撤退！走啊！{\r}\N\NEverybody out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.90,1:22:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到气闸去！跟我来！{\r}\N\NGet to the air lock! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.67,1:22:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班尼！快来啊！{\r}\N\NBenny, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.54,1:22:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 班尼！ - 我来了！{\r}\N\N- Benny! - I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.33,1:23:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}穿上宇宙飞行服，我们到外面去！{\r}\N\NPut these spacesuits on! we're going outside!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.94,1:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班尼，快点{\r}\N\NBenny, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.15,1:23:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恭喜你，魁德…{\r}\N\NCongratulations, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.95,1:23:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你终于带领我们找到了他{\r}\N\NYou led us right to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.52,1:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎能这么做！你也是个变种人{\r}\N\NHow can you do this? you're a mutant.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.25,1:23:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还有四个孩子要养{\r}\N\NI got four kids to feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.26,1:23:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第五个到哪里去了？{\r}\N\NSo what happened to number five?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.96,1:23:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈的，你终于抓到我的破绽了{\r}\N\NAh, shit, man. You got me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.56,1:23:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我根本就还没结婚{\r}\N\NI ain't even married.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.37,1:23:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在把手举起来！{\r}\N\NNow put your fucking hands in the air!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.41,1:24:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德…{\r}\N\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.01,1:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德…{\r}\N\NQuaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.41,1:24:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别白费力气了，兄弟 他的算命生涯已经结束了{\r}\N\NForget it, man. his fortunetelling days are over.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.72,1:24:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}启动…那个反应炉{\r}\N\NStart the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.62,1:24:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}解放火星…{\r}\N\NFree Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.43,1:24:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根先生想跟你谈谈{\r}\N\NMr. Cohaagen would like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.16,1:24:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原来这就是那位伟人{\r}\N\NSo this is the great man.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.47,1:24:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}难怪他总能躲过我们的耳目{\r}\N\NNo wonder he kept out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.74,1:24:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的好兄弟…{\r}\N\NWell, my boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.08,1:24:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是个英雄！{\r}\N\Nyou're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.21,1:24:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}操你的{\r}\N\NFuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.35,1:24:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不必谦虚，如今寡头已经死了！{\r}\N\NDon't be modest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.19,1:25:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叛军已全部被消灭 而你则是最大的功臣{\r}\N\NThe resistance has been completely wiped out, and you were the key to the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.52,1:25:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在骗人{\r}\N\NHe's lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.79,1:25:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这该死的两面人！{\r}\N\NYou two-faced bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.00,1:25:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别怪他，安其儿 他的确是无辜的{\r}\N\NYou can't blame him, angel. he's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.23,1:25:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是这样的，魁德… 我的手下没有一个能接近寡头{\r}\N\NYou see, Quaid, none of my people could get close to Kuato.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.61,1:25:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些该死的变种人 总是能闻出我们的气味{\r}\N\NFucking mutants could always sniff us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.61,1:25:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}于是豪瑟和我经过一番思考后 将你创造出来，一个完美的卧底计划{\r}\N\NSo Hauser and I sat down and invented you, the perfect mole.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.78,1:25:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你根本就是张眼说瞎话 豪瑟已经背叛了你{\r}\N\NYou know you're lying. hauser turned against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.69,1:25:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就是要让你这么想的{\r}\N\NThat's what we wanted you to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.99,1:25:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实是，豪瑟自愿来扮演道格?魁德{\r}\N\NThe fact is, Hauser volunteered to become Doug Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.89,1:25:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}唯有这方法才能骗过那些通灵人{\r}\N\NIt was the only way to fool the psychics.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.23,1:25:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别说笑了{\r}\N\NGet your story straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.73,1:25:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}自从我去过瑞可公司后 你手下这些白痴一直在追杀我{\r}\N\NThis idiot here has been trying to kill me ever since l went to Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.40,1:25:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么可能要杀你派去卧底的人{\r}\N\NYou don't kill somebody you're trying to plant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.67,1:25:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这并非计划中的一部份 是你自己要去瑞可而坏了事{\r}\N\NHe wasn't in on it. you set him off by going to Rekall.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.67,1:25:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那么为何我还活着？ - 我们一路上提供你许多帮助{\r}\N\N- So why am l still alive? - We gave you lots of help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.68,1:25:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 比方说班尼 - 这是我的荣幸，兄弟{\r}\N\N- Benny here. - My pleasure, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.55,1:26:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个拿手提箱给你的人，面具，钱{\r}\N\NThe guy with the suitcase, the mask, the money...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.32,1:26:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以及豪瑟所留的话… 这一切全是我们所安排的{\r}\N\Nthe message from Hauser, all of that was set up by us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.45,1:26:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，这说法太完美了{\r}\N\NSorry. Too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.09,1:26:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}完美个屁！{\r}\N\NPerfect, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.62,1:26:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在我们还没来得及派你上场前 就开启了你的记忆{\r}\N\NYou pop your memory cap before we can activate you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.33,1:26:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让瑞克特到处追杀你 破坏了我花了一年准备的计划{\r}\N\NRichter goes hog-wild, screwing up everything I spent a year planning.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.43,1:26:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老实说 这计划能成功连我都感到意外{\r}\N\NFrankly, I'm amazed it worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.57,1:26:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根…{\r}\N\NWell, Cohaagen...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.14,1:26:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真是服了你 这是我所听过最精彩的故事{\r}\N\NI have to hand it to you. It's the best mind-fuck yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.00,1:26:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不先别这么快就下结论{\r}\N\NWell, don't take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.44,1:26:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 某个你所信任的人要跟你说话 - 这一回又是谁？{\r}\N\N-Someone you trust wants to talk to you. -Who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.57,1:26:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我母亲？{\r}\N\NMy mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.61,1:26:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好，魁德{\r}\N\NHowdy, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.21,1:26:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你听见这段话 就表示寡头已死{\r}\N\NIf you're listening to this, that means Kuato is dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.68,1:26:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你也带领我们找到了他{\r}\N\Nand you have led us to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.22,1:26:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就知道你一定不会让我失望{\r}\N\NI knew you wouldn't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.99,1:26:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉让你吃了这么多苦头{\r}\N\NSorry for the shit I've put you through, but hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.46,1:26:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但朋友本来就该互相帮忙的{\r}\N\Nwhat are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.89,1:26:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很想祝你永远快乐，长命百岁，老朋友...{\r}\N\NI would like to wish you happiness and long life, old buddy...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.33,1:26:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但不幸的是，这是不可能的{\r}\N\Nbut unfortunately, this is not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.33,1:27:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要知道，你占用的身体是我的 我现在得要回来{\r}\N\NYou see, it's my body you've got there and I want it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.74,1:27:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，有借就有还 那身体本来就是我的{\r}\N\NSorry to be an Indian giver, but I was here first.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.21,1:27:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么，永别了，朋友{\r}\N\NSo adios, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.78,1:27:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你没让自己送命{\r}\N\NAnd thanks for not getting yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.18,1:27:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许咱们还会在梦里见面呢！{\r}\N\NHey, maybe we'll meet in our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.32,1:27:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁晓得会怎样？{\r}\N\NYou'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.06,1:27:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们这些混蛋！{\r}\N\NYou bastards!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放开我！{\r}\N\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.76,1:28:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 准备好了？ - 全检查过了{\r}\N\N- Ready? - Auto.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.13,1:28:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全准备好了，长官{\r}\N\N- Check. - Ready to go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.94,1:28:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放轻松点，魁德{\r}\N\NRelax, Quaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.37,1:28:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你会喜欢当豪瑟的 - 那家伙是个该死的混蛋！{\r}\N\N- You'll like being Hauser. - The guy's a fucking asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.68,1:28:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是真的 他是我最要好的朋友之一{\r}\N\NNot true. He's one of my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.97,1:28:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更何况他有一栋大房子，一辆宾土汽车{\r}\N\NBesides, he's got a big house and a Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.14,1:28:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你喜欢梅琳娜，对吧？ 你今后每晚都可以干她{\r}\N\NAnd you like Melina, right? You'll get to fuck her every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.18,1:28:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的… 她将成为豪瑟的心肝宝贝{\r}\N\NThat's right. She's going to be Hauser's babe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.35,1:28:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会打烂他的卵蛋{\r}\N\NI'll bust his balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.65,1:28:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，公主…{\r}\N\NUh-uh, princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.12,1:28:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要将你改变一下{\r}\N\NWe're having you fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.29,1:28:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你将学会尊敬，顺从…{\r}\N\NYou're gonna be respectful, compliant...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.76,1:28:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晓得该感激 这些都是女人该具有的美德{\r}\N\Nand appreciative. The way a woman should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.33,1:28:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根先生，你的电话{\r}\N\NMr. Cohaagen, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.20,1:28:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的，什么事{\r}\N\NYes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.67,1:28:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，G区的氧气已降到最低点{\r}\N\NSir. The oxygen level is bottoming out in Sector G.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.51,1:29:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要我接下来怎么做？{\r}\N\NWhat do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.94,1:29:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么也别做 - 但他们支持不到一个钟头了，长官{\r}\N\N- Don't do anything. - But they won't last an hour, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.25,1:29:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}管他们去死！{\r}\N\NFuck them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.38,1:29:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可以让别区的人作为警戒{\r}\N\NIt'll be a good lesson to the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.92,1:29:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别这样，科海根！你已达到你的目的 给这些人空气吧{\r}\N\NCome on, Cohaagen! You got what you want. give these people air.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.72,1:29:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的朋友，再过五分钟 你就不会关心这些人的死活了{\r}\N\NMy friend, in five minutes you won't give a shit about the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.56,1:29:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开始吧！大夫{\r}\N\NFire it up, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.83,1:29:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起！大夫{\r}\N\NExcuse me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.16,1:29:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他将会记得这一切吗？ - 完全不会{\r}\N\N- Is he gonna remember any of this? - Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.23,1:29:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的？{\r}\N\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.71,1:29:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了，魁德 我今晚要举行派对{\r}\N\NOh, Quaid, I'm having a party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.23,1:29:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你可以带梅琳娜一起来 提醒他一下，大夫{\r}\N\NWhy don't you and Melina drop by. Remind him, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.45,1:29:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我会的 - 派对上见了{\r}\N\N- Sure. - See you at the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.37,1:29:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别挣扎。你越反抗只会越痛苦{\r}\N\NKeep still. fighting just makes it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.67,1:30:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你不安静下来会精神错乱的{\r}\N\NIf you don't keep still, you'll end up psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.68,1:30:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不！{\r}\N\NHey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.09,1:30:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅琳娜，支持住！{\r}\N\NMelina, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.74,1:30:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还好吧？ 你仍是原来的你吗？{\r}\N\NAre you all right? Are you still you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.08,1:30:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也不怎么确定，亲爱的。你想呢？{\r}\N\NI'm not sure, dear. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.52,1:31:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}咱们快离开这里吧！{\r}\N\NLet's get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.35,1:31:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你得做个决定才行，长官{\r}\N\NYou have to make a decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.13,1:31:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杀了他{\r}\N\NKill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.70,1:31:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也该是时候了！{\r}\N\NIt's about goddamn time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.61,1:32:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要上哪去？ - 去找那反应炉{\r}\N\N- Where are you going? - To the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.34,1:32:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么反应炉？ - 在矿坑里的那个，快点！{\r}\N\N- What reactor? - The one in the mines. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.11,1:32:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些人都快死了啊！魁德 快停下来，我们得给他们空气{\r}\N\NPeople are dying, Quaid! Stop! We've got to get air!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.42,1:32:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那反应炉能制造空气 这就是科海根的大秘密，我们走{\r}\N\NThe reactor makes air. that's Cohaagen's secret. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.62,1:32:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个反应炉又是从哪来的？{\r}\N\NWhere's this reactor come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.32,1:32:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 外星人造的 - 外星人？{\r}\N\N- Aliens built it. - Aliens?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.23,1:32:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你确定它有用吗？ - 它就在前面{\r}\N\N- Are you sure about this? - It's just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.37,1:33:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被封住了{\r}\N\NWhat the hell--
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.16,1:33:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德！魁德！{\r}\N\NQuaid!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.16,1:33:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗨，魁德，你还记得我吧？{\r}\N\NHey, Quaid, you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.33,1:33:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是班尼，班尼就是我的名字{\r}\N\NBenny! Benny's the name! Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.78,1:33:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个厉害！{\r}\N\NOh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.98,1:33:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要把你们开膛破肚！{\r}\N\NI'm gonna drill you, sucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.18,1:34:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要把你们绞成肉泥！{\r}\N\NI'm gonna grind you up!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.49,1:34:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来了！{\r}\N\NI'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.56,1:34:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来找你了！宝贝{\r}\N\NI'm coming for you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.37,1:34:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这他妈的怎么回事？{\r}\N\NWhat the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.52,1:34:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个该死的火星废物！{\r}\N\NDamn this piece of Martian junk!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.89,1:34:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德，我要把你压扁！{\r}\N\NHey, Quaid, I'm gonna squash you!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.72,1:34:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}班尼，尝尝这个吧！{\r}\N\NBenny, here!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.83,1:34:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你他妈的在哪里？{\r}\N\NWhere the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.24,1:34:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我钻死你！{\r}\N\NScrew you!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.91,1:35:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德！快到这边来{\r}\N\NQuaid, get over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.25,1:35:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\N\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.58,1:35:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这边打通了一个缺口{\r}\N\NThere's an opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.05,1:35:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就知道{\r}\N\NI knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.38,1:35:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这整个东西 就是个以T矿制成的反应炉{\r}\N\NThis whole thing is one big reactor made out of terbinium.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.42,1:35:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}科海根知道它可以制造氧气 但那混蛋却不肯将它启动！{\r}\N\NCohaagen knows it makes air. the bastard won't turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.24,1:35:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然了{\r}\N\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.77,1:35:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果火星有了大气层，他就无法再统治了{\r}\N\NIf Mars had an atmosphere, he'd lose control.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.62,1:35:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看到那下面没？{\r}\N\NSee down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.29,1:35:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是一条冰河{\r}\N\NIt's a glacier.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.72,1:36:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}整个火星的核心都是冰{\r}\N\NThe whole core of Mars is ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.86,1:36:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}反应炉把冰融化{\r}\N\NThe reactor melts it...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.33,1:36:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就会释放出氧气来{\r}\N\Nand it releases the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.36,1:36:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧{\r}\N\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.63,1:36:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 足够让所有的人呼吸？ - 当然{\r}\N\N- Enough for everyone to breathe? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.80,1:36:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}足以供给整个星球使用{\r}\N\NEnough for the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.80,1:36:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果咱们能及时将它启动的话{\r}\N\NIf we turn it on on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.65,1:36:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上！快！{\r}\N\NCome on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.80,1:36:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}慢着{\r}\N\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.26,1:37:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开枪！{\r}\N\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.72,1:37:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}狗娘养的！{\r}\N\NSon of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.69,1:37:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快退开！{\r}\N\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.20,1:38:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他身上有全息国装置！{\r}\N\NHe's got a hologram!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.19,1:38:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们以为这是真的魁德吗？ 是真的{\r}\N\NYou think this is the real Quaid? It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.53,1:39:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要死也得带你一起死！{\r}\N\NNow, you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.44,1:40:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}派对上见了！瑞克特{\r}\N\NSee you at the party, Richter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.92,1:40:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别碰那东西！{\r}\N\NDon't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.35,1:40:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到一边去！退后！{\r}\N\NGet away! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.39,1:40:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怕什么？{\r}\N\NWhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.79,1:40:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 将它启动啊！ - 这是不可能的！{\r}\N\N- Turn it on. - Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.36,1:40:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一旦连锁反应产生 这星球上的T矿全将被毁{\r}\N\NOnce the reaction starts, it'll spread to all the terbinium in the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.56,1:40:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}整个火星也将熔毁{\r}\N\NMars will go into global meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.90,1:40:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以外星人才从未使用过它{\r}\N\NThat's why the aliens never turned it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.70,1:40:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你以为我会相信你吗？{\r}\N\NAnd you expect me to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.87,1:41:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁在乎你相不相信？ 再过30秒你就没命了{\r}\N\NWho gives a shit what you believe? In 30 seconds you'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.54,1:41:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后我将炸了这个地方 回家去吃麦片{\r}\N\NThen I'll blow this place up and be home in time for corn flakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.78,1:41:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我本来也不希望见到这种结局{\r}\N\NI didn't want it to end this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.62,1:41:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要豪瑟回来，但事与愿违…{\r}\N\NI wanted Hauser back. But no.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.02,1:41:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你偏要当魁德！{\r}\N\NYou had to be Quaid!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.29,1:41:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我本来就是魁德 - 你什么也不是！{\r}\N\N- I am Quaid. - You're nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.89,1:41:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你什么人也不是！ 只是一场愚笨的梦{\r}\N\NYou're nobody! You're a stupid dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.05,1:41:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的梦都是会结束的{\r}\N\NWell, all dreams come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.00,1:42:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}梅琳娜，别松手{\r}\N\NMelina, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.33,1:42:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不！别这么做！{\r}\N\NDon't do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.10,1:42:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们全都会死！{\r}\N\NWe'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.97,1:42:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的人通通会死！{\r}\N\NEverybody will die!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.46,1:43:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}魁德！{\r}\N\NQuaid!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.28,1:49:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真不敢相信，这就像一场梦{\r}\N\NI can't believe it. It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.11,1:49:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了？{\r}\N\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.75,1:49:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我刚刚想到一个可怕的念头。 如果这一切真的是一场梦呢？{\r}\N\NI just had a terrible thought. What if this is a dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.16,1:49:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就趁梦醒前赶快吻我吧！{\r}\N\NWell, then kiss me quick before you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.75,1:49:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}剧终{\r}

